org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor

Class ConfigurationAnnotationScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
      • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.ConfigurationAnnotationScanner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.objectweb.asm.Opcodes

    public class ConfigurationAnnotationScanner
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
implements org.objectweb.asm.Opcodes
    Class visitor detecting @Configuration annotation.

    After the visit, two state variables are set: isConfiguration is set to true if the class contained the @Configuration annotation parent is set to the parent class if and only if it's not a java.* class (which don't contain the Configuration annotation) and isConfiguration is set to false
